The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

NATION BRIEFS

 Chandigarh, July 30 (PTI): Dera Sacha Sauda head Gurmeet Ram Rahim Singh was today arrested and released after being questioned in a case in which he is accused of hurting the sentiments of Sikhs. 

 Police did not say whether Singh cooperated during the questioning. 

 Mumbai (PTI): The bomb disposal squad searched actor Jeetendras Juhu home after a news channel received an email saying a bomb has been planted there, police said on Monday. The same channel had received a hoax email threatening to blow up Amitabh Bachchans house around a fortnight ago.




